          <title>Reports: Pete Rose, baseball's all-time hits leader, dead at 83</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LAS VEGAS — Pete Rose, one of Major League Baseball's most polarizing athletes and the game's all-time hits leader, has died at the age of 83, according to TMZ. Rose's agent, Ryan Fiterman, confirmed the news to TMZ and said, "the family is asking for privacy at this time.]]></description>
